title: Free Coaching OCE community discord

embed.description: Check out the League Of Legends OCE community on Discord - hang out with 441 other members and enjoy free voice and text chat.

body: Join the League of Legends OCE discord to meet other players and improve your skills while having a great time. The free coaching is a dedicated channel where players can ask for coaching to help them drastically improve their ELO or higher skilled players can offer their assistance in helping new players improve. Come join today!
